ImageIcon p = ImageIcon(new URL("http://xys.com"));

or

ImageIcon p = new ImageIcon(filepath.xyz, description -can be null);

Cannot add ImageIcon to JPanel, must first add to JLable or something else. 
Cannot scale ImageIcon
Can Scale Image.
	getImage from ImageIcon
	Scale Image Object
		getScaledInstanceOf? returns scaled image. 
		Use image object to create another imageIcon with scaled image.
		
